text: Hey Everyone :wave: I'm Ben from Melbourne, Australia. Content Strategist for a small but growing content agency called SUDDENLY. Currently working on sharpening our customer value prop and brand positioning. We service clients from a number of different industries and sizes (National retailers and grocery chains through to B2B shipping container businesses). We're trying to sharpen how we talk about our services whilst balancing the fact we have a broad customer portfolio. Would love to hear peoples thoughts and experience on this broad but narrow deal. Also look forward to harvesting your brains I mean networking :alien: :face_with_cowboy_hat:
